resources.string: Get access to your timetable and never miss any class again!
Look if you are getting debarred in any subject!
Compare your marks and see if you can become 9 pointer!
Search for your faculty and get any information about them!
To see the welcome slider again, goto Settings -> apps -> welcome slider -> clear data
